'''Pak-kâ-siang''' (百家姓) he yit pún koân-yî [[Chûng-vùn]] [[siang-si]] ke [[sû]], chhai [[Pet-sung]] chhû-khì siá sṳ̀n. Ngièn sû-si̍p siang-si yù 411 chak, heu-lòi chen-pú to 504 chak, khì-chûng tân-siang 444 chak, fu-siang 60 chak.

Pak-kâ-siang, [[Sâm-sṳ-kîn]], lâu [[Chhiên-sṳ-vùn]] sâm-phu khiung-ha ham-cho "Sâm Pak Chhiên", he Chûng-koet kú-thoi se-ngìn-é ke khí-mùng thu̍k-vu̍t.

